---
import SubpageLayout from '../../../layouts/SubpageLayout.astro';

const FAQ = [
  {
    q: 'What does in-company AI training cost?',
    a: 'A training day costs EUR 2,500 to EUR 4,000, depending on group size and customisation. That includes preparation, materials and follow-up. Half-day sessions are possible; multi-day programmes are tailored to your organisation.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Which teams is the training suitable for?',
    a: 'Any team that will work with AI: board and management, marketing, HR, legal and development. Content and examples are adapted per audience. For developers there is a dedicated AI for Developers training.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Do you train outside the Netherlands?',
    a: 'Our home base is Groningen and most training happens on-site across the Netherlands, but we also run sessions elsewhere in Europe and remotely for distributed teams.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Which tools are covered?',
    a: 'The tools your team actually uses: ChatGPT, Claude, Copilot or European alternatives. The training focuses on tool-independent skills: writing effective prompts, judging output critically and handling company data safely.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Does this training count towards the EU AI Act literacy obligation?',
    a: 'The AI Foundations workshop covers much of the knowledge Article 4 of the EU AI Act asks for. If you need demonstrable compliance, look at our AI Literacy Training with certificates and documentation.',
  },
];

const PAGE_URL = 'https://aiheroes.io/en/services/incompany-ai-training';

const breadcrumbSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
  itemListElement: [
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://aiheroes.io/en' },
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Services', item: 'https://aiheroes.io/en/services' },
    { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 3, name: 'In-Company AI Training', item: PAGE_URL },
  ],
};

const faqSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'FAQPage',
  mainEntity: FAQ.map((item) => ({
    '@type': 'Question',
    name: item.q,
    acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: item.a },
  })),
};
---

<SubpageLayout
  lang="en"
  title="In-Company AI Training"
  subtitle="AI training at your location, for your team, with your cases. Across the Netherlands and beyond, from Groningen."
  seoTitle="In-Company AI Training | From €2,500 per day"
  seoDescription="In-company AI training for organisations: on-site, tailored to your team and sector. From AI Foundations to Copilot and AI literacy. Transparent pricing, across the Netherlands."
  accentColor="red"
  pillarBadge="Training"
  ctaLabel="Plan a training"
  trustedBy={["Postcode Loterij", "Banijay Benelux", "Tweede Kamer", "Philips Healthcare"]}
  jsonLd={[breadcrumbSchema, faqSchema]}
>
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <p class="text-xl text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      In-company AI training is the fastest way to make your whole team productive with AI. We come to your location, work with your documents and processes, and train until everyone applies it in their own work. More than 1,000 professionals went before you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-6">Why in-company beats an open course</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Generic AI courses stick to generic examples. In an in-company training your team practises on its own reality: your proposals, your customer questions, your data. That keeps the step from training to daily use small. It also lets you set safe data-handling agreements with the whole team at once.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-6">The programme</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-10 not-prose">
      <div class="border-2 border-stone-200 p-6 md:p-8 hover:border-brand-red transition-colors">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-1">AI Foundations</h4>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-red mb-3">Our core workshop · 1 day</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">The foundation for every team: how AI tools work, prompts that deliver results, judging output critically and building AI into daily work. The flagship of our training programme.</p>
        <a href="/en/services/training#ai-foundations" class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-red hover:underline underline-offset-2">More about AI Foundations &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 border-stone-200 p-6 md:p-8 hover:border-brand-red transition-colors">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-1">AI Literacy (EU AI Act)</h4>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-red mb-3">Article 4 obligation · ½-1 day</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Meet the literacy obligation of EU AI Act Article 4, with certificates and documentation per participant.</p>
        <a href="/en/services/ai-literacy-training" class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-red hover:underline underline-offset-2">More about AI Literacy Training &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 border-stone-200 p-6 md:p-8 hover:border-brand-red transition-colors">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-1">Copilot Training</h4>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-red mb-3">Microsoft 365 · ½ day</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">For organisations on Microsoft: get productive with Copilot in Word, Excel, Teams and Outlook.</p>
        <a href="/en/services/copilot-basics" class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-red hover:underline underline-offset-2">More about Copilot Training &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 border-stone-200 p-6 md:p-8 hover:border-brand-red transition-colors">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-1">AI for Developers</h4>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-red mb-3">Technical · 1 day</p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">AI tools and techniques for software teams: from AI-assisted coding to building with LLM APIs.</p>
        <a href="/en/services/ai-for-developers" class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-red hover:underline underline-offset-2">More about AI for Developers &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">€2,500-4,000</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Per training day</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">On-site</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Across the Netherlands</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">1,000+</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Professionals trained</div></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-6">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-10 not-prose">
      {FAQ.map((item) => (
        <div class="border-b border-stone-200 pb-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-lg mb-2">{item.q}</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.a}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="dark-box-content bg-brand-dark p-8 border-l-4 border-brand-red my-8 not-prose">
      <h3>AI training for your team?</h3>
      <p>Tell us about your team and goals and we will propose a programme. Within a week you know what the training covers, what it costs and when we can start.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SubpageLayout>
